LuminaUI - Biblioteca de UI via HubBar (CoreGui)
Uso:
local Library = loadstring(game:HttpGet("SUA_URL"))()
local Tab = Library:CreateTab({ Name = "Settings", Icon = "gear" })
Tab:AddSection("Player")
Tab:AddToggle({...})
Tab:AddSeparator()
Tab:AddButton({...})
